        About this item

        • ★ AMERICAN FLAGS FOR OUTSIDE 3X5: Authentic FMAA Certified American Flags for outside 3x5, proudly crafted and 100% Made in USA by USA Flag Co. As you hoist this remarkable 3x5 American flag and witness the iconic Red, White, and Blue Stars and Stripes waving in the sky, a deep sense of pride will resonate within your soul—declaring, "I'm Proud to be an American." Fly your US Flag with unwavering pride, showcasing your genuine allegiance to the land of the free and the home of the brave.
        • ★ USA FLAGS 3X5 PREMIUM DURABILITY: Embrace the highest quality in our best-selling American Flag 3x5 designed for all weather heavy duty outdoors. Crafted from robust heavy duty outdoor Made in USA nylon, it stands strong against high winds. Your United States Flag features sturdy polyester canvas headings reinforced by spurred brass grommets and a 4-point needle fly hem for lasting integrity. The 100% nylon material boasts a rich, lustrous appearance and exceptional wearing strength thanks to its superior strength-to-weight ratio. Experience the pride of a 3 x 5 American Flag that effortlessly flies in the slightest breeze.
        • ★ US FLAGS EMBROIDERED STARS AND SEWN STRIPES: Upgrade your patriotic display with our premium American Flag, boasting meticulously embroidered stars and flawlessly sewn stripes. Crafted for long-lasting durability, this flag is a symbol of quality and pride for your home or business. Elevate your space with the timeless beauty of our expertly crafted emblem.
        • ★ 3X5 AMERICAN FLAG FMAA CERTIFIED: Our 3x5 American Flag, proudly crafted by USA Flag, bear the esteemed certification of the FMAA. Crafted exclusively from domestic materials, our USA flags undergo a meticulous manufacturing process within United States facilities, employing U.S. labor at every stage. Experience the assurance of quality and authenticity as you proudly display a US flag 3x5 that embodies the true spirit of American craftsmanship.
        • ★ AMERICAN MADE FLAG: This American flag Made in USA serves as an excellent gift for friends or parents and is ideal for proudly showcasing at your home or business. Enhance the decor of your house, porch, wall, or office with this symbol of patriotism. Proudly display it at your residence or commercial business.
        • ★ BEST WARRANTY: Your Flag Pole Bracket comes with a (1 YEAR, NO QUESTIONS ASKED WARRANTY). Simply the Best... Buy the Right American Flags for the First Time from a Proud to be an American Company.

        Product Description

        American Flag - Made With Pride with U.S. Labor and Materials

        We are proud to say this beautiful American flag is produced in the United States, with American labor and materials. We strive to honor our tradition by investing in the most advanced technologies and processes to ensure that our US flags remain the standard of the flag business industry. Most importantly, by purchasing a USA Flag Co. Stars and Stripes flag you are supporting a dedicated team of the finest U.S. workers with a shared vision of designing and producing the highest quality hand-sewn products.

        USA Flag Co. United States Flags

        The Stars and Stripes Flags

        1. Craftsmanship by Americans for Americans
        2. They are constructed of tough 200-denier nylon
        3. Finished with heavy-duty canvas heading and thick brass grommets and a 4-needle fly hem
        4. American manufacturing and exceptional quality flag. The correct size, expertly reinforced, and diligently hand sewn and inspected.

        FMMA ( Flag Manufacturer’s Association of America )

        FMAA SEWN TAG - Labeled with FMAA tag which authenticates " Made in the U.S.A "

        Premium Nylon American Flag for Outside

        • Best resistance to UV radiation
        • Longest lasting nylon flag available
        • Lightweight, flies in the lightest breeze
        • Provides the brightest colors for a beautiful appearance

        Commitment to “100% Made in the USA”

        It is our philosophy and practice that this American Flag is made entirely of domestic materials and that each process in manufacturing the flag is accomplished in the United States with U.S. labor.

        • Honor our Troops, Active Duty Military, and Veterans
        • Show your support for our active and retired military personnel
        • Display this stunning symbol of freedom on your home or business
        • Complete assortment of American flags with Embroidered Stars and Sewn Stripes

        Show Your Support For Our Veterans

        By purchasing this USA Flag Co. American flag "Made in the USA" you are supporting U.S. employees right here in the United States of America and we want to say Thank You from the bottom of our hearts. We will always be grateful for your support! - Semper Fidelis

        Value = Quality + Flagship + American Craftsmanship

        Quality

        At every output point, USA Flag Co. delivers the highest quality products available. In addition to the manufacturing process, quality is also reflected in other attributes such as product availability, materials, packaging, and durability.

        Flagship

        EMBROIDERED STARS AND SEWN STRIPES

        The Nylon American flag is our success story. We built our reputation on this flag; it combines the beauty of fully embroidered stars and sewn stripes with the highest quality nylon fabric and color-matched thread for a beautiful flag that will fly smoothly in the lightest breeze. American craftsmanship construction, including 4-row stitching on the fly hems and a full 1/4” turn on all seams, will provide you with the best-wearing, longest-lasting nylon flag in the industry.

        American Craftsmanship

        Our flags are meant to last. USA Flag Co. uses a combination of the highest quality materials and state-of-the-art manufacturing to give you the best looking, precession designs and most durable flags in the industry.

        Thank You for supporting… A Veteran Owned Company !

        Patriotism: Love of and devotion to one's country. GOD Bless America!

            How customer reviews and ratings work

            Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
